Is your robot’s max speed 1 meter per second? Because that’s the fastest this code will tell it to go.

ChassisSpeeds’s vx and vy are in terms of meters per second, and omega in terms of radians per second:

github.wpilib.org

ChassisSpeeds (WPILib API 2024.3.1)

declaration: package: edu.wpi.first.math.kinematics, class: ChassisSpeeds

Joysticks return values between -1 and +1, with no associated units. Your code is taking those values and interpreting them as speeds.
